ZH: 这块大鱼有五斤重。
EN: This big fish weighs five 斤.

ZH: 他买了一斤苹果。
EN: He bought a 斤 of apples.

ZH: 我们需要两斤面粉来做蛋糕。
EN: We need two 斤 of flour to make a cake.

ZH: 这个包裹重了十斤。
EN: This parcel weighs ten 斤.

ZH: 请给我一斤猪肉。
EN: Please give me a 斤 of pork.

ZH: 我家的狗有二十斤重。
EN: My dog weighs twenty 斤.

ZH: 他刚买了一斤新茶叶。
EN: He just bought a 斤 of new tea leaves.

ZH: 这个西瓜有八斤重。
EN: This watermelon weighs eight 斤.

ZH: 练习举重可以增加你的斤数。
EN: Practicing weightlifting can increase your 斤.

ZH: 瓜子一斤三块，谁需要？
EN: Melon seeds, one 斤 for three dollars, who needs it?

ZH: 女生背三斤重的书包。
EN: The girl carries a three 斤 heavy school bag.

ZH: 这个宝宝才八斤重。
EN: This baby is only eight 斤.

ZH: 请问这个苹果多少一斤？
EN: Excuse me, how much is this apple per 斤?

ZH: 我每天做运动，已经减轻了两斤。
EN: I exercise every day and have already lost two 斤.

ZH: 菜市场的西红柿每斤只要一块钱。
EN: The tomatoes in the market are only one yuan per 斤.

ZH: 他今天背了三斤书走了十公里。
EN: He carried three 斤 books and walked ten kilometers today.

ZH: 他这次回来重了五斤。
EN: He gained five 斤 this time he came back.

ZH: 她穿着一双三斤的高跟鞋。
EN: She is wearing a pair of three 斤 high heels.

ZH: 桌上的苹果每斤售价是五块钱。
EN: The apples on the table are five yuan per 斤.

ZH: 家里的橘子每斤卖一块五毛。
EN: Oranges at home are sold for 1.5 yuan per 斤.
